text: Ðis is þaræ þriddan healfan hide boc æt æscforda & æt beohylle þe eadwig cing gebocode eadeage his þegne on ece yrfe.
Ðis synt þe land gemere to æscforda & to beohille.

Erest on won broces ford þonne andlang dices on luhhambeorh þonne on an rewæ þonon on ane dic þonon on annæ weg andlang weges on stanford þonon eft on anne weg oþ hit cymð eft an ane dic andlang dic to holon broces heafdum andlang broces on anne stanihtne ford þonon east on ane dic andlang dices to fileþleage forda up on stream on anne hagan andlang hagan on holancumbes land scare þonon on ane dic þonon on ruwan cnol þonon on anne hagan þonon on þet swelgend þonon on anne broc þonon to linor andlang linor to æscforda þonon to þere dic wale þonon on wiþig slæd þonon to holan broce of þam broce on ane dic.
Þonon eft on won broces ford.
Þonon is her butan þam gemæne les stræt.
Þonon synt þær manega hylla þæ man erien mæg.
